I've conducted a thorough analysis of your HTML code and identified several issues, particularly with the "Mirror bush" reference and other botanical inaccuracies. Here's my comprehensive review:

Major Issues Found

1. Mirror Bush Error

The code incorrectly mentions "Mirror bush" in two locations:

· In the flashcard set: "Prostrate - Coprosma repens" - This is correct
· In the root systems section: "Coprosma repens" - This is actually Mirror bush, which is:
  · Not prostrate in its typical form (can be upright)
  · Not Tasmanian native (it's native to New Zealand, naturalized in Tasmania)

2. Plant Classification Issues

Several species have incorrect family assignments:

· Athrotaxis selaginoides - Listed as Cupressaceae (should be Cupressaceae ✓ correct)
· Microcachrys tetragona - Listed as Podocarpaceae (should be Podocarpaceae ✓ correct)
· Diselma archeri - Listed as Cupressaceae (should be Cupressaceae ✓ correct)
· Eucalyptus globulus family is correct (Myrtaceae)
· Richea pandanifolia family is correct (Ericaceae)

3. Conservation Status Inaccuracies

· Lagarostrobos franklinii (Huon Pine) is listed as "Not Listed" but is actually Rare under TSP Act
· Phyllocladus aspleniifolius should be "Not Listed" ✓ correct

